New highlighter options in Notes Following your feedback we ve made it possible to choose from two types of highlighter in Notes: freehand which keeps your original handwritten stroke and smart which automatically aligns with both handwriting and typeset text. Easily remove highlights Use the highlighter no fill color to remove smart highlights or use the eraser to remove freehand highlights. Zoom level always displayed in Notes The zoom level is now always shown at the bottom left of the screen. Tap it to instantly reset the zoom to 100 . Zoom lock in Notes You can now lock and unlock the zoom as needed by tapping the lock icon next to the zoom level. Bug fixes As always we ve fixed bugs and fine tuned to enhance your Nebo experience. Cleaner notes with space reduction: Text conversion now removes extra space between paragraphs making your notes look as neat as digital documents.
